  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/04079d2cac7d0b924d8efe0bdf0d8ed6.poster.avif?t=1737691272\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/04079d2cac7d0b924d8efe0bdf0d8ed6.webm?t=1737691272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/04079d2cac7d0b924d8efe0bdf0d8ed6.mp4?t=1737691272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master Your Memory!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the ultimate memory challenge with over 1,000 unique cards! This isn't your average matching game – it's a brain-teasing adventure that will keep you coming back for more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/559aede112b7e1c2af83eb26c1cce0a2.poster.avif?t=1737691272\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/559aede112b7e1c2af83eb26c1cce0a2.webm?t=1737691272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/559aede112b7e1c2af83eb26c1cce0a2.mp4?t=1737691272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 Your Game, Your Way</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Three Game Modes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌸 Cozy Mode - Relax and play at your own pace</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏱️ Normal Mode - Test your skills against the clock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 Challenge Mode - Race the clock while matching cards in deceptively similar colors!</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable Difficulty Levels</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/99c12d6b97cd2a954ca88342ef4d69e1.avif?t=1737691272\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras_big/99c12d6b97cd2a954ca88342ef4d69e1.avif?t=1737691272 width=800 height=213 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎨 Endless Customization</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>20 Stunning Card Styles</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>30 Beautiful Backgrounds</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Selection of Music choices</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new looks with in-game currency earned through play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No microtransactions – everything is earned through gameplay!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/db0a86729f0a36fb82eec8d5ba4ba55c.poster.avif?t=1737691272\" width=800 height=516 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/db0a86729f0a36fb82eec8d5ba4ba55c.webm?t=1737691272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/db0a86729f0a36fb82eec8d5ba4ba55c.mp4?t=1737691272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📚 8 Themed Card Packs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match from these diverse collections:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 Activities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦁 Animals and Nature</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🍕 Food and Drink</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 Objects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😄 Smileys and People</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐ Symbols</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 Travel and Places</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎌 Flags</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/9293b103338d772b368d2bfb42a9e8ce.poster.avif?t=1737691272\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/9293b103338d772b368d2bfb42a9e8ce.webm?t=1737691272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/9293b103338d772b368d2bfb42a9e8ce.mp4?t=1737691272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏆 Features That Keep You Coming Back</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve Your Memory - See real improvements in your memory over time, trackable with the... :</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Leaderboards - Test your memory against other players worldwide! 💪🧠🥇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements - Over 20 challenging goals to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn Stars - Unlock new content through gameplay</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge mode - Put your memory to the test with this color specific mode!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/01920ae5692828986e65095d2a3024dc.avif?t=1737691272\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras_big/01920ae5692828986e65095d2a3024dc.avif?t=1737691272 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💫 Perfect For:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brain training enthusiasts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casual gamers looking for a challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Young gamers - Build focus, concentration, and cognitive skills while having fun! Perfect for parents looking for engaging educational gaming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players who love customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievement hunters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anyone looking to improve their memory skills</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/3a8b910878a7ebc332ca21f94a5d317d.poster.avif?t=1737691272\" width=554 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/3a8b910878a7ebc332ca21f94a5d317d.webm?t=1737691272\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297240/extras/3a8b910878a7ebc332ca21f94a5d317d.mp4?t=1737691272\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play now and put your memory to the test! 🎯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💌 A Note from the Developer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Originally a beloved 'Dreams' creation on the PS4, this memory game has been completely rebuilt and enhanced for Steam with new features, stunning visuals, and extended customization options. The community's enthusiasm for the Dreams version inspired me to bring this polished experience to PC players!</p>",
